116
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:38,040
Rasanya dia tak boleh lari kerana mencederakan pengikut Raja Iblis Carrion.

117
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:43,350
Awak janji tak buat kecoh tanpa kebenaran saya, kan?

118
00:07:43,476 --> 00:07:44,380
Eh?!

119
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:46,361
