133
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:28,826
Kau gelar saya "rendahan," tapi saya kuat daripada kau.

134
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,730
Saya tak kenal Raja Iblis Carrion.

135
00:08:32,730 --> 00:08:37,028
Tapi berdasarkan sikap kau, orang-orang saya akan memusuhi Carrion.

136
00:08:37,370 --> 00:08:41,964
Kau mahu bertanggungjawab kerana menjadi musuh seluruh Hutan Tebal Jura?

137
00:08:42,250 --> 00:08:44,210
